node.text:
My friend suddenly went, 'STAND HERE. This place is bokeh heaven.' & proceeded to take loads of portraits for me.
.
Not that I'm complaining. Bokeh heaven is always great. 🌚👍🏻 Memories aside, it's Moody Monday but always remember to keep smiling! 😁✨
.

Loveeeeeeeeee these lights and that brilliant focusing. This is the beeeeeeeeeeeest smile you can ever seen, keep up that cuuuteeee smiling all times. Hope you a greaaaat Monday and a beautiful new week dear!!

Beautiful!! Love the bokeh too! Gosh I miss photography has a past time and hobby. And I also miss traveling! Well, I'll have you know, I have been watching those virtual online tours lately. I know...its quite a strange experience. Hahahaha 😅😂. Meanwhile, I'm going to diligently apply for a job and start saving up. As soon as it is clear and safe to travel again, I am going to book my first flight out.
